= A generic type for classes that receive boolean values as results =

The BooleanOperationListener type allows a class to declare that it is able to
receive a boolean value as a result of an operation.

= to_event_receiver =

Wrap this event listener object to a standard EventReceiver object. Any boolean or
Error values will then be treated appropriately, and passed to the original object.

= on_boolean =

Called when a boolean operation has a boolean value to submit.
